{"title":"Java Basics","uid":"834aeb9ffdd87c27317f1a38c3063e2c","slug":"Java-Basics","date":"2022-11-15T03:13:16.000Z","updated":"2022-11-15T06:01:34.755Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java-Basics.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"The-Java-Programming-Language-and-the-Java-Platform\"><a href=\"#The-Java-Programming-Language-and-the-Java-Platform\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"The Java Programming Language and the Java Platform\"></a>The Java Programming Language and the Java Platform</h1><span id=\"more\"></span>\n<!-- markdownlint-disable MD041 MD002-->\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/topics/technologies/newtojava/programming-center.html\">https://www.oracle.com/topics/technologies/newtojava/programming-center.html</a></p>\n<p>Java 平台的两个主要组件是 Java 应用程序编程接口 (API)和将 Java 代码解释为机器语言的 Java 虚拟机 (JVM)。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yilongdong-blog.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/jvm.png\" alt=\"JVM\"></p>\n<p>API和JVM使得程序独立于硬件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://yilongdong-blog.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/javaplatform.png\" alt=\"Java Platform\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/getStarted/intro/definition.html\">Learn about the JVM and the APIs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Learn Java programming with <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/index.html\">The Java Tutorials</a>, a comprehensive source for Java language concepts. Object-oriented and Java programming are explained with graphics and code examples.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/java/newtojava/young-developers.html\">Young Developers </a>page summarizes the tools and learning resources for each software tool.</p>\n<p><strong>Recommended books:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>“Core Java, Volume I - Fundamentals (9th edition) by Cay Horstmann and Gary Cornell</li>\n<li>“Core Java, Volume II – Advanced Features (9th edition) by Cay Horstmann and Gary Cornell</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://shop.oreilly.com/product/9780596009205.do\">“Head first Java”</a> by Kathy Sierra and Bert Bates</li>\n<li>“Thinking in Java” by Bruce Eckel<br><a href=\"https://blogs.oracle.com/javamagazine/\">Oracle Java Magazine</a> book section</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","text":"The Java Programming Language and the Java Platform https://www.oracle.com/topics/technologies/newtojava/programming-center.html Java 平台的两个主...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":844,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":18,"path":"api/categories/笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#The-Java-Programming-Language-and-the-Java-Platform\"><span class=\"toc-text\">The Java Programming Language and the Java Platform</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"YiLongDong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"1数字图像处理-绪论","uid":"fd56f016e0cd406f4c293dabe662e43f","slug":"1数字图像处理-绪论","date":"2022-11-21T11:07:31.000Z","updated":"2022-11-21T11:07:56.645Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/1数字图像处理-绪论.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"点击阅读前文前, 首页能看到的文章的简短描述 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":26,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"课程","slug":"课程","count":2,"path":"api/categories/课程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数字图像处理","slug":"数字图像处理","count":1,"path":"api/tags/数字图像处理.json"}],"author":{"name":"YiLongDong","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"